graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>kserve-controller-manager]

    %% External Dependencies (Required/Conditional)
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt<br/>VirtualServices| Istio[Istio 1.19.x<br/>Service Mesh<br/>Conditional]
    KServe -->|serverless<br/>autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving 0.39.x<br/>Scale-to-Zero<br/>Conditional]
    KServe -->|TLS certs<br/>webhooks| CertManager[cert-manager latest<br/>Required]
    KServe -->|container<br/>orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.28.x<br/>Required]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KServe -->|model<br/>metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Metadata API<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -.->|mTLS<br/>sidecars| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio Integration<br/>Internal ODH]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Integration] -->|create/manage<br/>InferenceService| KServe
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Auto-deploy models] -->|deploy<br/>InferenceService| KServe

    %% External Services (Storage)
    KServe -->|model<br/>storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM]
    KServe -->|model<br/>storage| GCS[GCS Storage<br/>Google Cloud<br/>HTTPS/443 GCP SA]
    KServe -->|model<br/>storage| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>Microsoft Azure<br/>HTTPS/443 SAS Token]
    KServe -->|PVC<br/>mounts| PVC[Persistent Volume Claims<br/>Kubernetes Storage]

    %% Monitoring & Observability
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection] -->|scrape<br/>/metrics| KServe
    KServe -->|CloudEvents<br/>logging| CloudEvents[CloudEvents Broker<br/>Optional]

    %% Kubernetes API
    KServe -->|CRD<br/>reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token]

    %% Component Internal Architecture
    subgraph "KServe Components"
        Controller[Controller Manager<br/>Reconciles CRDs]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Validates/Mutates]
        StorageInit[Storage Initializer<br/>Downloads Models]
        ModelServers[Model Servers<br/>TensorFlow/PyTorch/SKLearn]
        Agent[KServe Agent<br/>Logging/Batching]
        Router[KServe Router<br/>InferenceGraph]

        Controller -->|validates| Webhook
        Controller -->|deploys| StorageInit
        Controller -->|creates| ModelServers
        Agent -.->|observes| ModelServers
        Router -->|routes to| ModelServers
    end

    %% Serving Runtime Templates
    KServe -->|pre-configured<br/>runtimes| ServingRuntimes[Serving Runtimes<br/>TensorFlow/Triton/MLServer/SKLearn<br/>XGBoost/TorchServe/HuggingFace]

